are it for planting. With 500,000 acres of irrigated farmland, the Imperial Irrigation District is the largest water district by volume in the United States and some of the most senior water rights to the Colorado River. According to western water law, the most senior water users have priority to use their water first during times of shortage. Decisions made in this district to share water cuts voluntarily — or form legal arguments to hold existing water rights — will have widespread impacts felt by millions in the Colorado River Basin.","lines":3,"showMoreText":"Read More","showLess":false,"wrapperProps":{"columnConfig":{"span":{"base":100,"md":20,"lg":16,"xxl":14},"start":{"md":3,"lg":5,"xxl":6}},"className":{"esc":"kGyAC","QWb":"HkWF"}}},"image":{"id":"010DJI_0819.jpg","showCopyright":"Please be respectful of copyright. Unauthorized use is prohibited.","alt":"","src":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/30a6356a-2c20-44f5-af28-a196b7d26fdf/010DJI_0819_3x2.jpg","sources":[{"src":{"x1":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/30a6356a-2c20-44f5-af28-a196b7d26fdf/010DJI_0819_3x2.jpg?w=374&h=249","x2":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/30a6356a-2c20-44f5-af28-a196b7d26fdf/010DJI_0819_3x2.jpg?w=748&h=498"},"max":374,"nativeWidth":374},{"src":{"x1":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/30a6356a-2c20-44f5-af28-a196b7d26fdf/010DJI_0819_3x2.jpg?w=413&h=275","x2":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/30a6356a-2c20-44f5-af28-a196b7d26fdf/010DJI_0819_3x2.jpg?w=826&h=550"},"max":413,"min":375,"nativeWidth":413},{"src":{"x1":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/30a6356a-2c20-44f5-af28-a196b7d26fdf/010DJI_0819_3x2.jpg?w=718&h=479","x2":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/30a6356a-2c20-44f5-af28-a196b7d26fdf/010DJI_0819_3x2.jpg?w=1436&h=958"},"max":767,"min":414,"nativeWidth":718},{"src":{"x1":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/30a6356a-2c20-44f5-af28-a196b7d26fdf/010DJI_0819_3x2.jpg?w=718&h=479","x2":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/30a6356a-2c20-44f5-af28-a196b7d26fdf/010DJI_0819_3x2.jpg?w=1436&h=958"},"max":1024,"min":768,"nativeWidth":718},{"src":{"x1":"https://i.natge